com.github.qacore.seleniumtestingtoolbox.pageobjects.factory

Class DefaultSeleniumFieldDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.qacore.seleniumtestingtoolbox.pageobjects.factory.DefaultSeleniumFieldDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openqa.selenium.support.pagefactory.FieldDecorator

    public class DefaultSeleniumFieldDecorator
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.openqa.selenium.support.pagefactory.FieldDecorator
    Default Selenium decorator for use with WebPageFactory or PageFactory. Will decorate:
    1. All of the WebElement fields
    2. All of the List<WebElement> fields
    The fields one and two fields that have @FindBy, @FindBys, or @FindAll annotation with a proxy that locates the elements using the passed in ElementLocatorFactory.
    Since:
    1.0.0
